name: GymWorkoutEDMmusic
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: gym music
des:
Can't find proper music for your gym workout? Try this skill to play hand-picked gym music to get you started. The skill is not a gym trainer. This skill will help you to play gym workout music which can be played for 1 hour. 

Try the skill by:
User: Alexa, open gym music
Alexa: Starting Gym music and have a great gym time. Please say start to play the audio.
User: start
Alexa: <plays the audio>

User: Alexa, open gym music
Alexa: Do you want to resume?
User: Yes (if you want to continue the music from last time) No (if you want to start complete playlist)
